        </item>
        <item>
            <title>医管局科技全面升级，地理围栏防病患走失、智能氧气樽提示医护换樽</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/01/ha-geo-fence/life-tech/smartcity/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ha-geo-fence</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/01/ha-geo-fence/life-tech/smartcity/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 05:20:53 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智慧城市]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AI]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1300593</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>医院管理局（医管局）推出多项科技措施，提升医疗服务质素。其中急症室陆续安装地理围栏定位系统，预计 2025 年底前全面启用，防止病人走失。此外玛丽医院重建项目首阶段将于今年内投用，引入智能药柜提升药物管理效率。智能氧气樽则计划扩展至所有医管局服务，确保气体及电池状态受监控。电子化共通平台已于去年底推行至全线医院，取代纸本记录纱布使用情况，并将进一步开发伤口评估功能。新一代早期事故通报系统亦即将推出，结合人工智能分析，促进员工反馈。</p><h2>地理围栏定位系统：守护病人安全</h2><p>医管局为应对病人走失问题，在急症室引入地理围栏定位系统。系统透过蓝牙手带监测病人位置，特别针对精神或认知障碍者。若病人接近出口，系统会发出警报，协助医护人员及时介入。据医管局资料，18 间公立医院急症室将于 2025 年底前完成安装。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1300594" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250401123037-694x437.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="437" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250401123037-694x437.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250401123037.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲地理围栏定位系统蓝牙手带，图片来源：RTHK</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1300595" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250401123041-694x447.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="447" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250401123041-694x447.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250401123041.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲地理围栏定位系统蓝牙手带，图片来源：RTHK</p><h2>智能装置提升效率</h2><p>玛丽医院重建项目第一期病房将于 2025 年内启用，新增智能药柜，让非办公时间的药物存取更安全及快捷。智能氧气樽同时现已应用于非紧急救护车服务，未来将推广至所有医管局服务范围。智能氧气樽能在氧气或电池不足时发出警报，确保病人安全。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1300596" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250401123124-694x458.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="458" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250401123124-694x458.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250401123124.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲智能氧气樽（右），图片来源：RTHK</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1300598" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250401123108-694x446.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="446" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250401123108-694x446.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250401123108.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲智能氧气樽，图片来源：RTHK</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1300599" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250401123510-694x454.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="454" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250401123510-694x454.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/20250401123510.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲智能氧气樽，图片来源：RTHK</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
